reut2-013.sgm, WRIGLEY &lt;WWY> RAISES GUM PRICE, SELLS NEW SIZE, Wm. Wrigley Jr. Co said it raised thewholesale price for seven-stick packages of its Spearmint,Juicy Fruit, Doublemint and Big Red brands, marchingcompetitive moves to a 35 cts retail price. The gum previouslysold at 30 cts a pack.    The company also said on March 30 it brought out afive-stick package of the four brands. The new package-size,generally phased out by the trade in 1972, was priced at 25 ctsa pack, Wrigley said. A company spokesman said the five-sticksize was well received" by the trade. Reuter&#3;

