reut2-013.sgm, BALDRIGE SEES NO TRADE WAR WITH JAPAN, U.S. Commerce Secretary MalcolmBaldrige said the dispute between the U.S. And Japan overcomputer chips will not develop into a full-scale trade war.    I think both sides will try and make sure that this doesn'tstart a trade war -- as a matter of fact I'm positive thatthere won't be a trade war with Japan

